{"title":"绿洲星空","authors":["黄秉荣"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":8,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿洲星空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄秉荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿洲星空的星星——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密云遮不住的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风沙扑不灭的深情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是神奇的明灯么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是璀璨的宝石么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装点在碧蓝的天幕上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿洲星空的星星哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深邃而又温柔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是美好憧憬的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直至陨落了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还拖着一缕微光——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给绿洲欢腾的黎明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在星座上眺望着北斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星光与星光相互映照——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪着圣洁的光焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪着圣洁的光焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一丝的嫉妒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一丝的倾轧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开拓者正像美丽的星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在自己的星座上——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵相映情谊相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵相映情谊相连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才开拓出这一片片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星空般壮美的绿洲。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}